Spin up your choice of virtual machine in under a minute

Droplet configurations provide flexibility to build, test, and grow your app from startup to scale. DigitalOcean provides a range of Droplet options that are built with one goal in mind: to ensure that no matter what you’re building or how you scale, you’ll have the right infrastructure to support you.

[Premium Basic](https://www.digitalocean.com/pricing/droplets#basic-droplets)

The most standard and flexible Droplet and configurable amount of memory

For simple or bursty apps: low-traffic web servers, blogs, discussion forums, CMS, small databases, dev/test servers, microservices, repository hosting, etc. Use Premium Droplets to ensure the use of modern processors from Intel and AMD.

[Premium General Purpose](https://www.digitalocean.com/docs/droplets/resources/choose-plan/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=education&utm_campaign=gettingstarted#dedicated-cpu-general-purpose-droplet)

The most popular modern Droplet, dedicated vCPU at 4GB memory each

For critical apps: high-traffic web servers, e-commerce sites, medium-sized databases, enterprise SaaS, etc. Premium General Purpose Droplets with Intel and AMD processors are also available.

[Premium CPU-Optimized](https://www.digitalocean.com/docs/droplets/resources/choose-plan/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=education&utm_campaign=gettingstarted#dedicated-cpu-cpu-optimized-droplet)

CPU-centric with dedicated vCPU at 2GB memory each

For CPU-intensive apps: CI/CD, video encoding, machine learning, ad serving, batch processing, active front-end web servers, etc. Premium CPU-Optimized Droplets with Intel and AMD processors are also available.

[Memory-Optimized](https://www.digitalocean.com/docs/droplets/resources/choose-plan/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=education&utm_campaign=gettingstarted#dedicated-cpu-memory-optimized-droplet)

Maximum memory with dedicated vCPU at 8GB memory each

For RAM-intensive apps: high-performance databases, in-memory caches, real-time big data processing, etc.

[Storage-Optimized](https://www.digitalocean.com/docs/droplets/resources/choose-plan/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=education&utm_campaign=gettingstarted#dedicated-cpu-storage-optimized-droplet)

With large amounts of NVMe SSD storage and memory and 100% dedicated vCPU

For extra-large apps: NoSQL databases (e.g. MongoDB), caches, and analytics workloads such as monitoring software and other data warehouses.

Follow our [recommended initial Droplet setup](https://www.digitalocean.com/docs/droplets/tutorials/recommended-setup/?utm_medium=email&utm_source=education&utm_campaign=gettingstarted) and get started.

